  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/f28201cd5db74aa3780fc9ef7bc02c5d.avif?t=1755745822\" width=616 height=137 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERVIEW</h2><strong>Dojo Masters</strong> is an indie fighting game with a heavy focus on representing the various Martial Arts.  The game is designed to be easy to pick up & play, but insanely difficult to master.  Unlike a traditional fighting game, you don't lose once your Stamina is depleted.  You must first deplete your opponent's stamina and then knock them down to win!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Easy To Play Insanely Difficult To Master</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/3433750b7f9874eaac1df4b98519f4a5.poster.avif?t=1755745822\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/3433750b7f9874eaac1df4b98519f4a5.webm?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/3433750b7f9874eaac1df4b98519f4a5.mp4?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each Martial Art challenges players in different ways while remaining quickly understandable. Every character uniquely adapts the attacks and techniques of their respective Martial Art<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play Online with Rollback Netcode</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/dcc9b149705b1a56916b0a0a08ff418e.poster.avif?t=1755745822\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/dcc9b149705b1a56916b0a0a08ff418e.webm?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/dcc9b149705b1a56916b0a0a08ff418e.mp4?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Challenge players from around the world through basic matchmaking or private lobbies, where you can customize your experience further.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hone your skills!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/918ff1eefb21bc30c9b56a99e0e6e863.poster.avif?t=1755745822\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/918ff1eefb21bc30c9b56a99e0e6e863.webm?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/918ff1eefb21bc30c9b56a99e0e6e863.mp4?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Save and review your replays with live rewind functionality, and test out different outcomes with Replay Takeover.  And for those who like to lab and get into the finer details, there are more than enough tools in Training Mode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4 Players (Local)</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/0c102c3ce26e0d30c9f384fe355e8581.poster.avif?t=1755745822\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/0c102c3ce26e0d30c9f384fe355e8581.webm?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/0c102c3ce26e0d30c9f384fe355e8581.mp4?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play Free-For-All with friends and or engage in Team Based Battles!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Additional Modes</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/851aac64889c9370e89379c821cba49e.poster.avif?t=1755745822\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/851aac64889c9370e89379c821cba49e.webm?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/851aac64889c9370e89379c821cba49e.mp4?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Engage in Game Modes ranging from Arcade Mode, Survival Mode, and Character Trials.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Steam Workshop Support</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/6a7b393d09d159ca07b44c77b7a7f151.poster.avif?t=1755745822\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/6a7b393d09d159ca07b44c77b7a7f151.webm?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538000/extras/6a7b393d09d159ca07b44c77b7a7f151.mp4?t=1755745822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Download, Create, and Share Custom Characters, Skins, and Stages!<br><br><br>",
